OL,7,FPublic Health Director Dr Nicola
OL,8,Fexplained that they cannot give exact
OL,9,Ffigures to protect islanders' privacy
OL,10,Fand confidentiality.
OL,12,FThe infected blood scandal has been
OL,13,Flabelled as the "worst treatment
OL,14,Fdisaster in the NHS", which saw more
OL,15,Fthan 30,000 people infected with HIV
OL,16,Fand Hepatitis C in the 1970s and 1980s.
OL,18,FDeputy Pursuant also asked what
OL,19,Fsupport victims received from Public
OL,20,FHealth and whether steps were taken to
OL,21,Fpursue compensation for islanders.
