OL,7,FHSC stated that victims "have received
OL,8,Fspecialist care and treatment from a
OL,9,FConsultant Virologist (...) with links
OL,10,Fto off-island providers at a national
OL,11,Fcentre of excellence for advice and
OL,12,Fsupport."
OL,14,FOn compensation, HSC said: "Officers
OL,15,Fwill continue to engage with UK
OL,16,FGovernment officials regarding the
OL,17,Festablishment of the compensation
OL,18,Fscheme and how it might extend to
OL,19,FBailiwick residents."
