OL,7,FThey warned, however, that further
OL,8,Fwork has been delayed until after the
OL,9,FUK's General Election on Thursday 4
OL,10,FJuly.
OL,12,FIan Walden, a victim of the infected
OL,13,Fblood scandal, says he was awarded
OL,14,F#20,000 from Guernsey's government
OL,15,Fbetween 2000 and 2008 and signed a
OL,16,Fwaiver that he couldn't claim anything
OL,17,Ffurther related to the scandal.
OL,19,FHowever, he is questioning whether he
OL,20,Fmay be entitled to compensation from
OL,21,Fthe UK government.
