OL,7,FHe has also said he has not received
OL,8,Fhelp from the consultant virologist.
OL,10,FIan explained: "I am relying on my GP
OL,11,Fwho has been absolutely brilliant and
OL,12,Fwas passed on under the Hemophilia
OL,13,FCentre at Southampton.
OL,15,F"The Social Security Department got me
OL,16,Fin contact with Professor Arthur in
OL,17,FRoyal Southants who looked after me
OL,18,Fand thankfully cleared my infection.
